SUMMARY:Godzilla Weekend: Mothra Madness - Mothra (1961)
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the theater for a mayoral proclamation video and a
  post-film discussion featuring a film scholar and organizer of the Bloom
 ington International Film Festival Matt Rice. The event also includes mer
 chandise from Badknees\, a live performance by Madam McVillian\, and appe
 arances by artist Matt Frank.
